reviews.text: Cheap and not at all cheerful Hong Kong style cafe
早餐麵好淋，食完半個鐘後即肚疴
管理麻麻，而且星期六、日唔應該加一收費！但熱奶茶好飲。
無半粒蕃茄肉醉，係素菜湯羅絲粉，
覺得沒有評論的這麼差吧，還是大家對商城美食街的標準比較高？

reviews.text:
Not punctual on departure. Best add 10-12 minutes in advance.
Operator kept reopening door (twice) at HK Station as more late passenger arrive outside closed door thus delaying everyone elee. Should just stick to the schedule and automation.
They are very convenient and efficient to use.  They are much better than the railway stations here in England.  You can travel to a lot of districts in HK and they come on time.

The place you buy octopus card. Prepare cash payment. 

Cool, clean and simple
The mtr officer there was rude. I asked her why my card got problem and to check my card balance with her handheld device.

I wonder how many mental unstable or pretending crazy in this city. I have seen few regulars staying at the unpaid area. They like to pick up the busiest time and jaywalked for attention in the station. Few times they bumped into people intentionally and walked away.  I strongly suggest people to report these mental unstable people to MTR staffs or police. That is definitely not right.

ここで航空機のチェックインと荷物を預けられます。ものすごく便利。
香港のほとんどのタクシーは運転が乱暴で乗り心地が悪いので、だいたい香港エクスプレスで行き来してます。

Not punctual on departure. Best add 10-12 minutes in advance.

They are very convenient and efficient to use.  They are much better than the railway stations here in England.  You can travel to a lot of districts in HK and they come on time.
預辦登機服務非常差，12月2號中午12點多EVA的八號櫃檯服務人員態度惡劣，自己普通話說不好，又不用英文問，我只是沒聽清楚有必要擺臉色嗎?不要說在香港，我在世界二十幾個國家幾乎沒看過這樣的服務。

에어포트익스프레스 표시판을 따라가세요.
그러면 도심공항.얼리체크인을 만날수 있습니다.
그리고 역 내 지하2층에는 환전소가 있으니 필요하신 분들 참고하세요.

수하물 외에 짐이 더 있으신분은 차라리 구룡역에서 얼리체크인하시고 짐보관라커 이용하셔서 짐 맡기고 홀가분하게 관광하시는게 나을듯합니다.어차피 공항갈때 다시 열차타러 와야하니 시내셔틀있는 구룡역추천합니다. 
그리고 공항 대기가 길어서 얼리체크인 하고가시면 진짜 30분은 덜서있습니다. 강추.
